The Luhya community will host a grand rally on January 18th to discuss Luhya unity and also marshal up their support for BBI and a powerful prime minister with 2 deputies. This was said when ODM leader Raila Odinga and western leaders were hosted by COTUsecretary general Francis Atwoli in Kwisero, Kakamega county. Elsewhere, ANC leader Musalia Mudavadi has insisted that he will be on the ballot come 2022.